
## Project Requirement List
1. Add complaints with a name and description.
2. Automatically categorize complaints based on predefined keywords.
3. Resolve complaints by providing a resolution.
4. Display all submitted complaints.
5. Sort complaints by date.
6. Save complaints to a CSV file.
7. Validate user inputs for complaint data.
8. Allow modification of complaint data.
9. Handle multiple categories like "Internet Issues", "Delivery", "Staff Behavior", and "General".
10. Provide a day-of-week calculation for complaint dates.
